  "title": "A multicolor UFO was spotted zigzagging between Luziânia and Ipameri-GO [1999]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/18/a-multicolor-ufo-was-spotted-zigzagging-between-luziania-and-ipameri-gp-1999/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-v6",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>JAN 23rd, 1999</strong>. Time: 10h40 pm. Duration: 15 minutes. Between the cities of Luziânia and Ipameri, State of Goiás, an unidentified flying object with the appearance of bright red, blue and green lights, and the size of an airplane, was spotted by two people. According to the witnesses, the UFO was observed zigzagging in the Southwest direction at an altitude of approximately 10km and flying at 500km / h.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.534. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado entre Luziânia e Ipameri, Goiás”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
